<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ARC Estudio Creativo — Catálogo</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --ink:#0C1310;
    --paper:#F7F5EF;
    --forest:#163832;
    --forest-2:#1F4D42;
    --sage:#A9C9B8;
    --pop:#4ADE80;
    --line: rgba(12,19,16,0.12);
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}

  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}

  body{
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    line-height:1.5;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }

  h1,h2,h3{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing:-0.02em;
  }

  .mono{
    font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing:0.02em;
  }

  a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}

  /* ---------- layer-line motif ---------- */
  .layers{
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      var(--line) 0px,
      var(--line) 1px,
      transparent 1px,
      transparent 10px
    );
  }

  /* ---------- header ---------- */
  header{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:20px 6vw;
    background:rgba(247,245,239,0.85);
    backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .brand{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
  }

  .brand img{
    height:34px;
    width:auto;
    display:block;
  }

  nav{display:flex; gap:32px;}
  nav a{
    font-size:0.85rem;
    font-weight:500;
    color:var(--forest);
    position:relative;
    padding-bottom:4px;
  }
  nav a::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; left:0; bottom:0;
    width:0%; height:2px; background:var(--pop);
    transition:width .25s ease;
  }
  nav a:hover::after{width:100%;}

  /* ---------- hero ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    padding:9vh 6vw 10vh;
    background:var(--forest);
    color:var(--paper);
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero::before{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; inset:0;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(247,245,239,0.05) 0px,
      rgba(247,245,239,0.05) 1px,
      transparent 1px,
      transparent 14px
    );
    pointer-events:none;
  }

  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    font-size:0.75rem;
    color:var(--pop);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:0.14em;
    margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{
    content:"";
    width:20px; height:1px;
    background:var(--pop);
  }

  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-weight:700;
    max-width:14ch;
    line-height:1.02;
  }

  .hero p{
    margin-top:26px;
    max-width:46ch;
    font-size:1.05rem;
    color:var(--sage);
  }

  .hero-meta{
    margin-top:56px;
    display:flex; gap:48px; flex-wrap:wrap;
    position:relative;
  }
  .hero-meta div{border-left:1px solid rgba(247,245,239,0.25); padding-left:16px;}
  .hero-meta .val{font-family:'Space Grotesk'; font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:600;}
  .hero-meta .lab{font-size:0.72rem; color:var(--sage); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.08em; margin-top:4px;}

  /* ---------- intro strip ---------- */
  .intro{
    padding:64px 6vw;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:60px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .intro h2{font-size:1.6rem; max-width:16ch;}
  .intro p{color:#3A423E; max-width:52ch;}
  @media(max-width:800px){.intro{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}

  /* ---------- catalog ---------- */
  .catalog{padding:70px 6vw 100px;}
  .catalog-head{
    display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:44px;
    flex-wrap:wrap; gap:16px;
  }
  .catalog-head h2{font-size:2rem;}
  .catalog-head .count{font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--forest-2);}

  .grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap:2px;
    background:var(--line);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  @media(max-width:760px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}

  .card{
    background:var(--paper);
    padding:36px;
    display:flex; flex-direction:column;
    transition:background .25s ease;
  }
  .card:hover{background:#EFEDE4;}

  .card-visual{
    aspect-ratio:4/3;
    background:var(--forest);
    border-radius:4px;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .card-visual svg{width:100%; height:100%;}

  .card-tag{
    position:absolute; top:12px; left:12px;
    font-size:0.65rem;
    color:var(--pop);
    background:rgba(12,19,16,0.5);
    padding:4px 8px;
    border-radius:20px;
  }

  .card h3{font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:8px;}
  .card .desc{color:#3A423E; font-size:0.92rem; margin-bottom:20px; flex-grow:1;}

  .specs{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top:14px;
    gap:8px;
  }
  .specs div{font-size:0.68rem;}
  .specs .k{color:#7A8580; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; display:block; margin-bottom:3px;}
  .specs .v{color:var(--ink); font-size:0.78rem;}

  .price-row{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    margin-top:22px;
  }
  .price{font-family:'Space Grotesk'; font-weight:600; font-size:1.15rem;}
  .cta-mini{
    font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600;
    color:var(--forest);
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--forest);
    padding-bottom:2px;
  }

  /* ---------- footer / cta ---------- */
  .contact{
    background:var(--ink);
    color:var(--paper);
    padding:90px 6vw;
    text-align:center;
    position:relative;
  }
  .contact h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem); max-width:20ch; margin:0 auto 20px;}
  .contact p{color:var(--sage); max-width:44ch; margin:0 auto 34px;}
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    background:var(--pop);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-weight:600;
    padding:14px 28px;
    border-radius:4px;
    font-size:0.9rem;
  }

  .contact-links{
    margin-top:26px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    gap:28px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .contact-links a{
    font-size:0.85rem;
    font-weight:600;
    color:var(--pop);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--pop);
    padding-bottom:2px;
  }
  .contact-links a:hover{color:var(--paper); border-color:var(--paper);}
  .contact-links .mono{font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--sage);}

  footer{
    padding:26px 6vw;
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    background:var(--ink);
    color:var(--sage);
    font-size:0.75rem;
    border-top:1px solid rgba(247,245,239,0.1);
    flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="brand">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="ARC Estudio Creativo">
  </div>
  <nav>
    <a href="#catalogo">Catálogo</a>
    <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <span class="eyebrow">Estudio de impresión 3D &amp; diseño</span>
  <h1>De la idea<br>al objeto.</h1>
  <p>Piezas impresas a medida, accesorios funcionales para el hogar y desarrollos por encargo. Cada producto nace como archivo digital y termina siendo algo que podés tocar.</p>

  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div>
      <div class="val mono">100%</div>
      <div class="lab">Diseño propio</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="val mono">FDM</div>
      <div class="lab">Tecnología de impresión</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="val mono">B2B</div>
      <div class="lab">Comisiones a pedido</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="intro">
  <h2>Un catálogo de muestra, no una tienda.</h2>
  <p>Esta página reúne los productos que diseñamos e imprimimos en ARC. Sirve para mostrar el trabajo, no para comprar online: si algo te interesa, escribinos directamente y coordinamos el pedido a medida.</p>
</section>

<section class="catalog layers" id="catalogo">
  <div class="catalog-head">
    <h2>Catálogo</h2>
    <span class="count mono">04 piezas en exhibición</span>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">

    <!-- Hub Desk -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-visual">
        <span class="card-tag mono">HUB-01</span>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect width="400" height="300" fill="#163832"/>
          <g stroke="#A9C9B8" stroke-width="1.4">
            <rect x="70" y="150" width="260" height="70" rx="6"/>
            <line x1="70" y1="168" x2="330" y2="168"/>
            <line x1="70" y1="186" x2="330" y2="186"/>
            <line x1="70" y1="204" x2="330" y2="204"/>
            <circle cx="110" cy="130" r="16" stroke="#4ADE80"/>
            <line x1="110" y1="114" x2="110" y2="150"/>
            <rect x="150" y="118" width="34" height="32" rx="3"/>
            <rect x="200" y="100" width="18" height="50" rx="2"/>
            <rect x="230" y="112" width="18" height="38" rx="2"/>
            <rect x="260" y="106" width="18" height="44" rx="2"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Hub Desk</h3>
      <p class="desc">Organizador modular de escritorio: centraliza cargador, lápices, celular y accesorios chicos en una sola base impresa.</p>
      <div class="specs">
        <div><span class="k mono">Material</span><span class="v mono">PLA+</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Medidas</span><span class="v mono">18×9×6cm</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Color</span><span class="v mono">A pedido</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-row">
        <span class="price">Consultar</span>
        <span class="cta-mini">Pedir →</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tetris balance set -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-visual">
        <span class="card-tag mono">TET-02</span>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect width="400" height="300" fill="#163832"/>
          <g stroke="#A9C9B8" stroke-width="1.4">
            <rect x="140" y="190" width="120" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#4ADE80"/>
            <rect x="160" y="160" width="30" height="30"/>
            <rect x="190" y="160" width="30" height="30"/>
            <rect x="190" y="130" width="30" height="30"/>
            <rect x="220" y="100" width="30" height="30"/>
            <rect x="130" y="130" width="30" height="30"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Tetris Balance Set</h3>
      <p class="desc">Set de piezas apilables inspiradas en el clásico Tetris, pensado como juego de equilibrio y objeto decorativo de escritorio.</p>
      <div class="specs">
        <div><span class="k mono">Material</span><span class="v mono">PETG</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Piezas</span><span class="v mono">7 bloques</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Color</span><span class="v mono">A pedido</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-row">
        <span class="price">Consultar</span>
        <span class="cta-mini">Pedir →</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Inflated phone stand -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-visual">
        <span class="card-tag mono">INF-03</span>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect width="400" height="300" fill="#163832"/>
          <g stroke="#A9C9B8" stroke-width="1.4">
            <path d="M140 200 C130 150, 160 110, 200 110 C240 110, 270 150, 260 200 C260 215, 140 215, 140 200 Z" stroke="#4ADE80"/>
            <rect x="175" y="90" width="50" height="80" rx="10" transform="rotate(-8 200 130)"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Soporte Inflable</h3>
      <p class="desc">Soporte de celular con perfil curvo tipo "inflado", liviano y estable, para escritorio o mesa de luz.</p>
      <div class="specs">
        <div><span class="k mono">Material</span><span class="v mono">PLA+</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Medidas</span><span class="v mono">9×6×5cm</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Color</span><span class="v mono">A pedido</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-row">
        <span class="price">Consultar</span>
        <span class="cta-mini">Pedir →</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mini Stack -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-visual">
        <span class="card-tag mono">MST-04</span>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect width="400" height="300" fill="#163832"/>
          <g stroke="#A9C9B8" stroke-width="1.4">
            <rect x="150" y="190" width="100" height="24" rx="3"/>
            <rect x="160" y="160" width="80" height="24" rx="3"/>
            <rect x="170" y="130" width="60" height="24" rx="3" stroke="#4ADE80"/>
            <rect x="180" y="100" width="40" height="24" rx="3"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Mini Stack</h3>
      <p class="desc">Set de bandejas apilables en tamaños decrecientes para organizar objetos chicos: anillos, clips, pastillas, cables.</p>
      <div class="specs">
        <div><span class="k mono">Material</span><span class="v mono">PLA+</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Niveles</span><span class="v mono">4 bandejas</span></div>
        <div><span class="k mono">Color</span><span class="v mono">A pedido</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-row">
        <span class="price">Consultar</span>
        <span class="cta-mini">Pedir →</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="contact" id="contacto">
  <h2>¿Te interesa alguna pieza o querés algo a medida?</h2>
  <p>Escribinos cotización o comisión — coordinamos material, color y plazos según lo que necesites.</p>
  <a class="btn" href="mailto:arc.estudio3d@gmail.com">Escribir a ARC →</a>
  <div class="contact-links">
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/arc.estudiocreativo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
    <span class="mono">342 526 3538</span>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <span>© 2026 ARC Estudio Creativo</span>
  <span class="mono">Catálogo</span>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
